import birriataco from '../../images/image1.jpeg';
import truckmenu from '../../images/truckmenu.png';
import danandjuan from '../../images/danandjuan.jpg';

export const homeObjOne = {
    id: 'home',
    lightBg: false,
    lightText: true,
    lightTextDesc: true,
    topLine: 'Home',
    headline: 'Traditional Jalisco Style Beef Birria',
    description: 'Sign up for our mailing list to receive notifications on our progress and locations once our food truck is up and running.',
    buttonLabel: 'Place Order',
    imgStart: false,
    img: birriataco,
    alt: 'Grilling',
    dark: false,
    primary: true,
    darkText: true
};

export const homeObjTwo = {
    id: 'menu',
    lightBg: true,
    lightText: false,
    lightTextDesc: false,
    topLine: 'Menu',
    headline: 'Menu Items Below',
    description: 'Burritos, Tacos, Nachos, Fries',
    buttonLabel: 'Place Order',
    imgStart: true,
    img: truckmenu,
    alt: 'Grilling',
    dark: false,
    primary: true,
    darkText: true
};

export const homeObjThree = {
    id: 'about',
    lightBg: false,
    lightText: true,
    lightTextDesc: true,
    topLine: 'About',
    headline: 'Family owned and operated',
    description: 'The idea to start a food truck started during the middle of the pandemic, looking for something to do with lockdown and because he had severely twisted my ankle in April of that year, Juan started cooking more and more and found a real passion for it and at the same time had been talking with his brothers, Daniel and Luis, about starting a business. Naturally, a food truck seemed like a good idea and so weve been working on making that a reality.',
    imgStart: false,
    img: danandjuan,
    alt: 'Grilling',
    dark: false,
    primary: true,
    darkText: true
};
